title: Flight SiImulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Flybywire A320 - terrain map added to ND
description:
In this video we will have a look at the terrain map functionality which has been added to the latest developer version of A320 from FlyByWire. Keep in mind that this functionality is still work in progress and might still have some issues. If you want to use this functionality make sure you have installed the developer edition and not the "normal" edition of the A320.
